end_makelog¶

end_makelog(paths)¶

Appends to file makelog, recording end time.

Note

We technically allow for writing to a make log even after the make log has ended. We do not recommend this for best practice.

Parameters

paths (dict) – Dictionary of paths. Dictionary should contain values for all keys listed below.

Path Keys

makelog (str) – Path of makelog.

Returns

Return type

None
